caption: Opening in a strip mall in the corner of Sawtelle Blvd. and Santa Monica blvd. There is also a 7-11, Sushi Stop, Subway, Donut Bakery, and a Key Smith located with the strip mall. Across the street  is a gas station, and also a movie theater. Located by the 405 S. entrance and exit and also 405 N. entrance  of Santa Monica blvd.
